trans-unit.source: Provides a design-time editor in a design host such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um editor de tempo de design em um host de design como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WizardStepCollectionEditor"></xref> class using the given <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WizardStepCollectionEditor"> </xref> classe usando o determinado <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of items in the collection.
Indicates whether multiple instances may be selected.
trans-unit.target: Indica se várias instâncias podem ser selecionadas.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if multiple items can be selected at once; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Se vários itens podem ser selecionados de uma vez; Caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This implementation always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Essa implementação sempre retorna <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new form to display and edit the current collection.
trans-unit.target: Cria um novo formulário para exibir e editar a coleção atual.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm> to provide as the user interface for editing the collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>para fornecer como a interface do usuário para editar a coleção.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.CollectionForm>

trans-unit.source: Creates an instance of the collection of the specified <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma instância de coleção especificado <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the data types this collection can contain.
trans-unit.target: Recupera os tipos de dados, que essa coleção pode conter.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation looks in the collection for the Item property and returns the returning Type of the item.
trans-unit.target: A implementação padrão de pesquisa na coleção para a propriedade do Item e retorna o tipo de retorno do item.

trans-unit.source: Instead, use the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.NewItemTypes%2A> property of the base class.
trans-unit.target: Em vez disso, use a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.NewItemTypes%2A>propriedade de classe base.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CollectionEditor.NewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the CreateNewItemTypes method to override the default implementation.
trans-unit.target: Use o método CreateNewItemTypes para substituir a implementação padrão.
